quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  67,27,so jab woh dekh len ge ke woh ( wada ) qareeb agaya to kafiroon ke munh buray ho jaien ge aur ( un se ) kaha jaye ga ke yeh wohi hai jis ke tum khawastgah they
  67,28,kaho ke bhala dekho to agar khuda mujh ko aur mere sathiyon ko halaak kardey ya hum par meharbani kere. to kon hai kafiroon ko dukh dainay walay azaab se panah day ?
  67,29,keh do ke woh jo ( khuday-e ) rehman ( hai ) hum isi par imaan laaye aur isi par bhrosa rakhtay hain. tum ko jald maloom hojaye ga ke Sarih gumraahi mein kon par raha tha
  67,30,kaho ke bhala dekho to agar tumhara pani ( jo tum peetay ho aur bartay ho ) khushk hojaye to ( khuda ke ) siwa kon hai jo tumahray liye sheree pani ka chashma baha laaye
  68,1,noon. qalam ki aur jo ( ahal qalam ) likhte hain is ki qasam
  68,2,ke ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum apne perwar-digaar ke fazl se deewany nahi ho
  68,3,aur tumahray liye be intahaa ajar hai
  68,4,aur ikhlaq tumahray bohat ( aali ) hain
  68,5,so anqareeb tum bhi dekh lau ge aur yeh ( kafir ) bhi dekh len ge
  68,6,ke tum mein se kon deewana hai
  68,7,tumhara perwar-digaar is ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo is ke raste se bhatak gaya aur un ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo seedhay rastay par chal rahay hain
  68,8,to tum jhutlanay walon ka kaha nah maanna
  68,9,yeh log chahtay hain ke tum narmi ikhtiyar karo to yeh bhi naram ho jaien
  68,10,aur kisi aisay shakhs ke kahe mein nah aajana jo bohat kasmain khanay wala zaleel auqaat hai
  68,11,ta'an aamaiz ishartein karne wala chughlian liye phirnay wala
  68,12,maal mein bukhal karne wala hadd se barha howa badkaar
  68,13,sakht khoo aur is ke ilawa bud-zaat hai
  68,14,is sabab se ke maal aur betay rakhta hai
  68,15,jab is ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunai jati hain to kehta hai ke yeh aglay logon ke afsaanay hain
